          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">
            Tailwind CSS vs CSS-in-JS: Which to Choose?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm mb-4">
            A detailed comparison between Tailwind CSS and CSS-in-JS solutions for your next projects.
